9. Common Mistakes
Mistake 1

Direct Modification

❌ Wrong

count = count + 1;

✅ Correct

setCount(count + 1);


Mistake 2

Forgetting Import

❌

const [count, setCount] = useState(0);

Without import.

✅

import { useState } from "react";


Mistake 3

Using State Like Normal Variable

❌

count++;

✅

setCount(count + 1);

